{
  "stem": "1828.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 228.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And one of the things he had to-- to do-- everybody had to do some work there, which was good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I found out later on, in-- in the concentration camps, that the worst way to exist is not to have anything to do at all, and just watch it happen.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I remember, I saw him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He had a mop, and he was supposed to clean-- it was either the latrine or the-- I don't know what he was cleaning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I-- and I was very upset about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he said, this is the best job around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You do your job well, and you do it quickly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then the rest of the day, I can learn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He still had his books, and he had his tefillin at that time still.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that filled his day, and was-- he didn't complain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Food was not bad compared to later on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And it was-- there was a-- a Jews' elder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We had ghetto money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We had a group of fantastically able and talented people-- musicians and all kind of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we started putting on plays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there were painters there who drew pictures well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There's some of the Theresienstadt artists preserved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And-- but then after a little while, I might mention that in that place of 8-- that held 8,000 people before the war, when we were there, there were about 60,000 Jews crammed into this place.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But we had our own doctors and our own people around who-- who took orders from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- but they were invisible, and it was a self-- sort of self-administered existence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that-- that--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that was not a show place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the regular Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people that were officials there had a right to-- to put you on a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
